/** * Репозиторий для работы с упражнениями и результатами */ interface ExerciseRepository { suspend fun getExercisesByType(type: ExerciseType): Flow<List<Exercise>> suspend fun getExercisesByGrade(grade: Grade): Flow<List<Exercise>> suspend fun getExerciseById(id: String): Result<Exercise?> suspend fun saveExerciseResult(result: ExerciseResult): Result<Unit> suspend fun getUserResults(userId: String): Flow<List<ExerciseResult>> suspend fun getUserResultsForExercise(userId: String, exerciseId: String): Flow<List<ExerciseResult>> }

